Technical Details
Programming Language

Java (JDK 8+)

Core Concepts Used

Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

Abstraction (abstract Product class)

Inheritance (ElectronicsProduct, ClothingProduct, BookProduct)

Polymorphism (dynamic discount calculation using overridden methods)

Encapsulation (private fields with controlled access)

Architecture & Design

Layered package-based structure for modularity:

products – product hierarchy and business logic

cart – shopping cart and cart item management

orders – order processing and GST calculation

customer – customer and cart association

Menu-driven console application

Loose coupling between components using object composition

Data Structures

ArrayList

Used for managing cart items and orders

Custom objects

Product, CartItem, Order, Customer

Functional Features

Category-based discount calculation using polymorphism

Dynamic user input using Scanner

Shopping cart operations:

Add products

Update quantities

Calculate totals

Order management

Unique order ID generation

GST (18%) calculation

Stateless order processing

Exception Handling

Basic input handling using Java Scanner

Can be extended to handle invalid inputs and stock validation

Tools & Environment

IDE: IntelliJ IDEA / Eclipse / VS Code

Version Control: Git & GitHub

Build Tool: Java compiler (javac)

Extensibility

Easy to extend with:

Database integration (JDBC)

REST APIs (Spring Boot)

Web UI (HTML/CSS/JS)

Payment gateway integration
